==English==
===Verb===
'''[[tell]] [[off]]'''

# {{idiom}} To speak to somebody [[rudely]], [[disrespectfully]] or [[angrily]]; to [[berate]]; to [[unleash]] one's [[fury]] verbally towards somebody.
#:''You should have heard her in there, '''telling off''' the guy whose fault it was!''

